snippet.title: The Sims 3: Town Life Stuff | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sims™ 3 Town Life Stuff* introduces venues complete with dozens of new objects to give your Sims' town and homes a makeover. 

Customize a new library, an exclusive gym, a fun playground, or a fresh laundry room. Your Sims get more than new décor and style options—they get new community venues, like Scrumptious Nibbles Café, for your Sims to visit too!

* Require The Sims 3 to play.
